            <div style="margin-top: 60px;">
                <h2 id="track-interactions">Track User Interactions</h2>
                <p>Track how users interact with articles, including clicks and other engagement metrics.</p>

                <h2 id="analyze-time">Analyze Reading Time</h2>
                <p>Measure the amount of time users spend reading specific topics to refine their preferences.</p>

                <h2 id="adjust-recommendations">Adjust Recommendations</h2>
                <p>Automatically update recommendations based on user click and interaction behavior.</p>

                <h2 id="save-categories">Save and Rank Categories</h2>
                <p>Allow users to save their favorite categories and rank them based on their preferences.</p>

                <h2 id="update-feedback">Update Preferences via Feedback</h2>
                <p>Refine user preferences based on explicit feedback, such as liking or disliking articles.</p>

                <h2 id="recommend-articles">Recommend Similar Articles</h2>
                <p>Recommend articles similar to those the user has previously read and liked.</p>

                <h2 id="display-recommendations">Display Recommended Articles</h2>
                <p>Show a curated list of recommended articles tailored to the user's interests.</p>

                <h2 id="exclude-categories">Exclude Categories</h2>
                <p>Provide options to exclude certain categories or topics from the recommendation feed.</p>

                <h2 id="predict-interest">Predict New Articles</h2>
                <p>Use historical data to predict new articles that may interest the user.</p>

                <h2 id="adapt-preferences">Adapt to Changing Preferences</h2>
                <p>Dynamically adjust recommendations as user preferences evolve over time.</p>
            </div>
